title: Ep. - 190 - KARY BRITTINGHAM FROM REAL HOUSEWIVES OF DALLAS
description:
Kary Brittingham is the newest cast member on Real Housewives of Dallas. She talks about her childhood, appearing on Below Deck, getting cast for the show, LeeAnne’s wedding, and more. 

 

Kate’s 6 year old daughter answers a series of reality tv questions.
